(Source: Dispatch time: January 20, 2007 22:53)Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, January 20. The National Financial Work Conference was held in Beijing from January 19 to 20.The main task of this meeting was to summarize the financial work of the last few years, to analyze current financial situation, to unify ideological understanding, and to map out overall financial work over the coming years.Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China Central Committee and Premier Wen Jiabao, members of the Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China Central Committee and Vice-Premiers Wu Yi, Zeng Peiyan, Hui Liangyu, members of the Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China Central Committee and State Councilors Zhou Yongkang and Cao Gangchuan, State Councilors Tang Jiaxuan, Hua Jianmin, and Chen Zhili attended the meeting.Wen Jianbao first provided a comprehensive conclusion of the financial work in the past few years in his speech.He pointed out that financial work has made significant achievements since 2002. The financial sector has developed rapidly and soundly. Financial reforms have made major steps and various financial functions have played bigger roles. The opening up of the financial sector is steadily expanding. Financial monitoring and legislation has significantly strengthened. The entire financial sector has witnessed historical changes. It plays an important supporting and facilitating role in economic and social development.Wen Jiabao pointed out that many contradictions and issues still exist in current financial sector that mainly include unsound financial system, unreasonable financial structure, poor governance and operation mechanisms of financial institutions, accelerating international trade imbalance, and quite a number of hidden financial dangers.Great importance must be attached to this and forceful measures should be adopted to resolve the problems.Wen Jiabao stressed that our nation's financial reform and development is facing a new situation. The financial sector is at a momentous turning point and a crucial development stage.The urgency and responsibility to succeed in financial work must be enhanced, efforts must be devoted to push financial reform and development to a new phase, financial reform should be deepened in all areas, and continuous sound and safe development of the financial industry should be encouraged in order to make greater contributions to the realization of sound and rapid development of the national economy and the building of a Socialist harmonious society.Wen Jiabao indicated that financial reform and development shoulder heavy tasks at present and in the future. Overall planning should be made, key points should be emphasized, and efforts should be devoted to the follow work.(1) Continue to deepen reform of state-owned banks and to accelerate the establishment of modern banking system.Continue to deepen the reform of the Industrial and Commercial Bank of China, the Bank of China, the China Construction Bank and the Bank of Communications and to consolidate and optimize development and reform results. The keys are to continue to improve corporate governance, to accelerate operational change mechanism, and to deepen reforms in branches and grass-roots.The shareholding reform of the Agricultural Bank of China must be advanced in a steady and orderly manner and its market orientation and responsibility to serve the three agricultural areas must be enhanced. Overall restructuring must be implemented to fully utilize the capital, network, and professional advantages in the counties to better serve the three agricultural areas and the counties' economies.Reform in banking policy must be pushed forward based on the principles of classified guidance and 'one bank one policy'.Reform of the China Development Bank will be implemented first with full implementation of commercial operations that will mainly engage in medium and long-term businesses.Open and transparent tenders must be administered in policy-related businesses.Reforms in other commercial banks and financial assets management companies must be pressed forward without delay.(2) Accelerate rural financial reforms and improve rural financial system.Adopt effective measures in various aspects and improve financial services for rural areas to provide strong financial support for the building of Socialist modern rural area.Facilitate the establishment of sound multi-level, wide-coverage, and sustainable rural financial system that suits the characteristics of the three agricultural areas.Improve rural financial organization system to give full play to the capacities of commercial finance, policy-related finance, cooperative finance, and other financial organizations.Further innovations in rural financial organizations, moderately adjust and relax access policy of financial organizations in rural area, lower access threshold, encourage and support development of multiple ownership financial organizations that suits rural demands and characteristics and to actively foster diversified small-scale credit organizations.At the same time, step up and improve monitoring to prevent risks and hidden dangers.Aggressively promote innovations in rural financial products and services and to actively develop rural insurance.Enhance policy support for rural finance.(3) Vigorously develop capital and insurance markets to construct multi-level financial market system.Expand scale and proportion of direct finance.Reinforce building of foundation system of capital market, make effort in improving quality of listed companies, rigorously enforce information disclosure system, and enhance transparency.Speed up the growth of bond market.Expand corporate bond issuing scale, firmly develop corporate bonds, and improve bond governance system.Further advance reform and development in insurance industry, expand insurance service areas, improve insurance service standard, and increase risk-prevention awareness and ability.(4) Give full play to the service and adjustment functions of finance to stimulate coordinated economic and social developments.Further enhance the foresight, scientificness, and effectiveness of financial adjustments, reasonably adjust total currency and credit volume, optimize credit structure, and facilitate steady and rapid development of the economy.Increase the financial support for small and medium-sized enterprises, self-innovation projects, social causes, and underdeveloped regions.Steadily promote interest rate market reform.Further improve Renminbi foreign exchange rate formation system, step up foreign exchange reserves operation and management, actively explore and expand channels and ways in using foreign exchange reserves.Adopt comprehensive measures to facilitate basic equilibrium in balance of payments.(5) Vigorously and cautiously advance the opening up of the financial sector to the outside.Concentrate on the optimization of the open structure of the financial sector and steadily facilitate opening up of the capital market.Promote fair competition between domestic and overseas financial institutions.Continue to promote financial cooperation between the mainland, Hong Kong, and Macau.(6) Enhance financial monitoring ability and strengthen internal governance of financial institutions to ensure financial stability and security.Improve the augmented supervision system and mechanism of finance and enhance monitory coordination and cooperation.Step up financial monitoring measures, perfect financial legal system, tighten the effective control of cross-border short-term capital flow especially of speculative capital, step up anti-money laundering measures, continue to deepen efforts in rectifying and regulating financial order.Wen Jiabao emphasized in the end that Party and government leadership of financial work should be strengthened to provide strong assurance to the sustained sound and safe development of the financial sector.Insist on the separation of the government and corporations, consciously handle matters in accordance to economic laws, financial laws, and market laws, and safeguard the autonomy in operation of financial institutions to the full.Concentrate on improving the ideological and political quality, professional skills, and professional ethics of employees to build a high-quality contingent of financial staff.Severely punish all corruption and criminal behaviors.All areas and departments must actively support the work of the financial departments.State Councilor Hua Jianmin presided over the meeting and delivered the concluding speech, as well as put forward explicit demands for the implementation of the spirit of the meeting.He stressed that all areas, departments, and all financial systems must unify their ideological understanding to the decisions and planning in financial work of the Central government. They should clarify the tasks, emphasize the key points, carefully organize, and strengthen coordination to realistically carry out various financial tasks, policies, and measures.People who attended the meeting include leading members of the people's governments and heads in charge of financial work in all provinces (autonomous regions, and municipalities directly under the Central government), leading members of the people's governments and heads in charge of financial work in cities with separate budget from central finance and those in the Xinjiang Construction Corps, leading members of relevant departments under the State Council, and heads of relevant units and departments of the financial system.Heads of the Central government of the Communist Party of China, the National People's Congress, relevant departments under the National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference, the Supreme People's Court, and the Supreme People's Procuratorate were also invited to attend the meeting.(The end)